 <!-- contact_left start here-->
 <div class="contact_left">
  <p>
   The Beckman Institute is a multi-disciplinary research center
   <br>
    for research in the chemical and biological sciences.
    <br>
     The Institute was dedicated in 1989 with funds from the
     <br>
      <a href="http://www.beckman-foundation.com/" title="Arnold and Mabel Beckman Foundation">
       Arnold and Mabel Beckman Foundation.
      </a>
     </br>
    </br>
   </br>
  </p>
 </div>
 <!-- contact_left ends here-->
 <!-- contact_right start here-->
 <div class="contact_right">
  <p>
   California Institute of Technology
   <br/>
   1200 E. California Blvd.
   <br/>
   Pasadena, California 91125
   <br/>
   (626) 395-6811
  </p>
